name: Toni Peterson
about: Toni Peterson is a Hematologist in Comilla. His qualification is MBBS, BCS (Health), MD (Hematology). He is a Consultant in the Department of Hematology at Cumilla Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Comilla Trauma Center. Practicing hour of Dr. Saqi Md. Abdul Baqi at Comilla Trauma Center is 3pm to 6pm (Closed: Friday).

name: Randolph Pate
about: Randolph Pate is a Endocrinologist in Dhaka. His qualification is MBBS (Dhaka), BCS (Health), MACP (USA), MD (Endocrinology & Metabolism) (BSMMU). He is a Consultant in the Department of Diabetes & Hormone at Sheikh Hasina National Institute of Burn & Plastic Surgery. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Green Life Hospital, Dhaka. Practicing hour of Dr. Md. Shayedat Ullah at Green Life Hospital, Dhaka is 6.30pm to 10pm (Closed: Thu & Friday).

name: Jillian Vang
about: Jillian Vang is a Colorectal Surgeon in Dhaka. His qualification is MBBS, FCPS (Surgery), FACS (USA), FRCS (UK), Fellow- Colorectal Surgery ( Japan). He is a Assistant Professor in the Department of Surgery at Dhaka Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Popular Diagnostic Center, Dhanmondi. Practicing hour of Dr. Md. Ibrahim Khalil (Shahin) at Popular Diagnostic Center, Dhanmondi is 5pm to 8pm (Sat, Mon, Tue, Wed & Fri).

name: Samantha Lamb
address: 363 Trucklemans Lane, Dante, District Of Columbia, 1968
about: Samantha Lamb is a Plastic Surgeon in Dhaka. Her qualification is MBBS, MS (Plastic Surgery). She is a Plastic Surgeon in the Department of Plastic Surgery at Sheikh Hasina National Institute of Burn & Plastic Surgery. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Super Specialized Hospital. Practicing hour of Dr. Tamanna Ahmed at Super Specialized Hospital is 6pm to 9pm (Closed: Friday).

name: Sophie Brown
about: Sophie Brown is a Plastic Surgeon in Dhaka. Her qualification is MBBS, FCPS (Surgery), MS (Plastic Surgery). She is a Associate Professor in the Department of Plastic Surgery at Tairunnessa Memorial Medical College & Hospital. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Medinova Medical Services, Malibagh. Practicing hour of Dr. Munny Momotaz at Medinova Medical Services, Malibagh is 6pm to 8pm (Sun, Mon, Tue & Thu).

He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Zainul Haque Sikder Women's Medical College & Hospital. Practicing hour of Dr. S. M. Ayub Hossain at Zainul Haque Sikder Women's Medical College & Hospital is 4pm to 7pm (Sun, Tue & Thu).

name: Bettye Greer

He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Al Helal Specialized Hospital. Practicing hour of Dr. Tanmoy Prakash Ghosh at Al Helal Specialized Hospital is 6pm to 8pm (Sat & Thu).

name: Greer Calderon
about: Greer Calderon is a Orthopedic Surgeon in Sylhet. His qualification is MBBS, MS (ORTHO). He is a Professor & Head in the Department of Orthopedics Surgery at Jalalabad Ragib-Rabeya Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Popular Medical Center & Hospital, Sylhet. Practicing hour of Prof. Dr. Cyrus Shakiba at Popular Medical Center & Hospital, Sylhet is 5pm to 8pm (Closed: Friday).

name: Aimee Mayer
about: Aimee Mayer is a Orthopedic Surgeon in Sylhet. His qualification is MBBS, D-ORTHO. He is a Assistant Professor in the Department of Orthopedic Surgery at North East Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at North East Medical College & Hospital. Practicing hour of Dr. Md. Mahin at North East Medical College & Hospital is 10am to 1.30pm (Sat, Tue, Wed, Thu).

name: Dale Ochoa
about: Prof. Dr. Dale Ochoa is a Cardiac Surgeon in Narayanganj. His qualification is MBBS, MS (CVTS). He is a Professor in the Department of Cardiovascular & Thoracic Surgery at Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Popular Diagnostic Center, Narayanganj. Practicing hour of Prof. Dr. Md. Aslam Hossain at Popular Diagnostic Center, Narayanganj is 10am to 1pm (Only Friday).
